season_start.catgirl_line_1: Omniguardian, since this is our first encounter, why don't you sit down and have some tea with me?
season_start.catgirl_line_2: How was your adventure today? I hope this cup of tea brings you tranquility. We can continue our journey tomorrow.
season_start.catgirl_line_3: Today's tea snacks are a bit special. I hope you like them. The Wonderland also has special surprises waiting for you to discover.
season_start.catgirl_line_4: My friend, continue your exploration. The treasures of the Wonderland are nearby, but you'll need to search carefully to find them.
season_start.catgirl_line_5: Enjoy this cup of tea. True sweetness often reveals itself slowly at the end.
season_start.catgirl_line_6: Dear friend, I'm about to unveil the true secret of the Wonderland to you. Look forward to that moment.
season_start.catgirl_line_7: Omniguardian, you've uncovered the final gift of the Wonderland. From now on, I'll be by your side every single day.
season_start.season_start_tower_des1: Clearing higher floors in Rift Odyssey grants greater rewards.
season_start.hero_70389_des: AoE Shield, DMG RED on Low HP
